menuPanel

Interface Listener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventListener, KeyListener, MouseListener, MouseMotionListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ControlsMenuListener, GameMenuListener, GameOverMenuListener, GamePanelListener, LevelsMenuListener, LoadingMenuListener, MenuListener, OptionMenuListener, VictoryMenuListener

    public interface Listener
extends MouseListener, KeyListener, MouseMotionListener
    L'interfaccia Listener rappresenta il generico ascoltatore mouse e tastiera per i menu.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Gualtieri Stefano, Gagliardi Alessandra, Morelli Lorenzo, Cuconato Francesco
